#+title: Configurações Emacs

#+begin_src emacs-lisp
(setq inhibit-startup-message t)
#+end_src

* Configurações Gerais

** Desabilitar tela de boas vindas

#+begin_src emacs-lisp
  (menu-bar-mode -1)
#+end_src

** Configuracao da interface

#+begin_src emacs_lisp
  (menu-bar-mode -1)
  (tool-bar-mode -1)
  (scroll-bar-mode -1)
  (tooltip-mode -1)
  (set-fringe-mode 10)
  (column-number-mode 1)
  (save-place-mode 1)
  (recentf-mode 1)
  (savehist-mode 1)
#+end_src


